  "name": "RPlog_Axel_and_Tyler_Again",
  "title": "Axel and Tyler Again",
  "summary": "The Sith Lord Malign -- known also as Tyler Damion -- stalks into the rough Smuggler's Den looking for action, where the smuggler Axel Vichten sits drinking with his nervous companion Khanar. As a side group of patrons including Keifan, Kinsa'una, and the Imperial traitor Alana Ten'ou makes its exit, Malign settles in across from Axel and the two old associates trade barbed words. Malign coldly reminds Axel that he never delivers hollow threats and that the smuggler lives only so long as he remains useful to the Sith, while Axel insists his loyalties go to whoever provides the best deal and that a broken bargain was no fault of his own. Khanar bristles at the Sith's menace but holds his tongue, eventually rising alongside Axel to meet Malign's gaze. Malign departs with his drink untouched and a final ominous warning, leaving Axel to sigh that he has no idea whether his words landed, while a disgusted Khanar drowns his nerves in a pitcher of ale.",
